column5: well here i go again    im going to give it another try in the morning,i was talking to a few of the port darlington salmon crew,and they got a few decent fish today & tonight,so im going to give it another try and hopefully i can do better than the other day,going to try a new color atomik trolling fly,and prob put some lead core 5 color out to,so i will hopefully have a few nice pics and a good report when i come back....and oh ya theres an empty seat as well....cheers
Good luck on your outing - I'll be watching for the report and pictures.  Don
Good luck Shawn.But I dont Know whow you will out do the last outing.Dan
all the best! hoping to get out that way in a few weeks
Good luck out there, If the weather holds up I think I'm gonna head out there Thursday. Never fished out of Darlington. Mostly just here out of Whitby..
